shell-tools

The rpm installs all scripts into /usr/sbin/

cadduser -  utility for adding a single user to a virtual site.  

caddvsite - adding a virtual site 

cdeluser - deletes a user 

cdelvsite  - deletes a virtual site

clistuser - lists all users

clistvsite - lists all virtual sites

cmoduser - modify a user

cmodvsite - modify a virtual site

The usage for these commands can be found by giving --help arg.
